# OnThisDay.PH Marketing Website ‚Äî Project Rules

## Project Overview

Static marketing website for [OnThisDay.PH](https://onthisday.ph), a civic tech platform helping Filipinos fact-check historical claims. Built with Astro as a zero-JS static site, separate from the main app.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Astro 6.0.4
- **CSS**: Tailwind CSS v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite` (NOT a config file)
- **Language**: TypeScript strict mode
- **Content**: Astro Content Collections + Zod
- **Deployment**: Vercel ‚Äî production at `https://onthisday.ph`
- **Package Manager**: pnpm (required), Node.js >= 22.12.0

## Development Commands

```bash
pnpm dev      # http://localhost:4321
pnpm build    # production build ‚Üí dist/
pnpm preview  # preview built site
```

No test suite ‚Äî verify with `pnpm build`.

## Architecture Rules

### Components
- All components are `.astro` files in `src/components/`
- Always define a typed `interface Props` in component frontmatter
- Zero client-side JS ‚Äî this is a static site, no hydration unless absolutely needed
- `BaseLayout.astro` is the **only** layout ‚Äî never create another

### BaseLayout Props (required)
```typescript
interface Props {
  title: string;       // required
  description: string; // required
  ogImage?: string;
  type?: 'website' | 'article';
  publishedDate?: string; // ISO string, blog posts only
}
```

### Tailwind v4 ‚Äî Critical Rules
- Config lives in `src/styles/global.css` under `@theme {}` ‚Äî **NOT** in `tailwind.config.js`
- Brand colors (always use these):
  - `ph-blue` = `#0038A8`, `ph-blue-dark` = `#002A7F`
  - `ph-red` = `#CE1126`, `ph-red-dark` = `#A80D1E`
  - `ph-yellow` = `#FCD116`
- Custom utility classes (already defined in `global.css`):
  - `.gradient-border-card` ‚Äî hover gradient border card
  - `.animate-on-scroll` / `.animate-on-scroll-delay-1` / `.animate-on-scroll-delay-2`
  - `.animate-on-scroll-scale`, `.animate-pulse-glow`, `.animate-float`, `.animate-float-delay`, `.animate-count-up`

### Blog Posts ‚Äî Content Collections
Posts in `src/content/blog/*.md` require this exact frontmatter (Zod-validated):
```yaml
---
title: "Post Title"
description: "One-sentence SEO summary"
date: "YYYY-MM-DD"
author: "OnThisDay.PH"  # optional
---
```
Slug = filename. Missing fields = build failure.

### File Routing
```
src/pages/index.astro        ‚Üí /
src/pages/about.astro        ‚Üí /about
src/pages/blog/index.astro   ‚Üí /blog
src/pages/blog/[slug].astro  ‚Üí /blog/<slug>
src/pages/404.astro          ‚Üí 404
```

## What NOT to Do

- No React/Vue/Svelte ‚Äî intentionally zero-JS
- No `tailwind.config.js` ‚Äî config is in `global.css`
- No new layouts ‚Äî only `BaseLayout.astro`
- No hardcoded secrets ‚Äî `.env` is gitignored
- No pushing directly to `main` ‚Äî use pull requests

## Adding Features

**New page**: `src/pages/<name>.astro` + use `BaseLayout` + update `Header.astro` / `Footer.astro` nav
**New component**: `src/components/<Name>.astro` + typed `interface Props` + use brand colors
**New blog post**: `src/content/blog/<slug>.md` + all required frontmatter fields

